            port 1|         |
            ..    | ------> |
            port n|         |
            ------+

        p1, p2, p3, p4 = (
            config.ports.port(name="txp1", location=utils.settings.ports[0])
            .port(name="txp2", location=utils.settings.ports[1])
            .port(name="rxp1", location=utils.settings.ports[2])
            .port(name="rxp2", location=utils.settings.ports[3])
